Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! Tennis Court Sizes STANDARD_DOUBLE = 1 STANDARD_SINGLE = 2 CUSTOM_DOUBLE = 3
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
if gs_cont_pen<=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if line_cont_pen<=0 then parameters line_cont_pen=4
if gs_fill_pen<=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91 if line_fill_pen<=0 then parameters line_fill_pen=91 if runout_fill_pen<=0 then parameters runout_fill_pen=91
values{2} "iCourtSizeType" STANDARD_DOUBLE, `Стандартный Двойной`, STANDARD_SINGLE, `Стандартный Одиночный`, CUSTOM_DOUBLE, `Специальный Двойной`
if iCourtSizeType <> CUSTOM_DOUBLE then if iCourtSizeType = STANDARD_DOUBLE then B = 18.2880 else B = 15.5448 endif
parameters B = B lock "A", "B" endif
